## Key Product Facts

**6 Assessment Dimensions:**
| Dimension | Weight | Key Focus |
|---|---|---|
| Shadow AI | 25% | Unauthorized AI tool usage |
| Vendor Risk | 25% | Third-party AI exposure |
| Data Governance | 20% | AI data handling + flows |
| Security & Compliance | 15% | Policy enforcement gaps |
| AI-Specific Risks | 10% | Model-level failure risks |
| ROI Tracking | 5% | Measuring AI investment return |

**Maturity Profiles:** Experimenter, Builder, Innovator, Achiever
**Questions:** 252 total (10 per dimension per profile, 13 for AI-Specific Risks)
**Timing:** Under 5 minutes per dimension, under 30 minutes for all six

**Scoring thresholds:**
- 0-30: Critical risk
- 31-60: High risk
- 61-80: Moderate risk
- 81-100: Low risk

**Vendor score thresholds:** 0-30 Renew | 31-60 Renegotiate | 61-80 Remediate | 81-100 Replace

